title: Up next: Sharks at Devils - Devils
text:
Sharks at Devils 
Today, 7 p.m.
TV: MSG Plus. Radio: WFAN-AM 660/FM 101.9.
Story line: Coach Pete DeBoer returns to Prudential Center for the first time since being fired by the Devils on Dec. 26 of last season. His Sharks are off to a 3-0-0 start and have outscored opponents 12-1. The Devils (0-3-0) are looking for their first win under coach John Hynes.
